   <h4 className=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-white mb-2 leading-relaxed\">GraphQL Apollo Client Setup</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-sm text-white/80 line-clamp-2\">Snippet for initializing the Apollo Client with authentication headers and cache persistence.</p>\n            <div className=\"mt-4 flex items-center text-white text-xs font-medium opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">\n              View Snippet <ChevronRight className=\"w-4 h-4 ml-1\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"bg-purple-700 p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:border-white/40 transition-all cursor-pointer group relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(126,34,206,0.5)]\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n              <span className=\"px-2 py-1 bg-white/20 text-white text-[10px] rounded uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">Business</span>\n              <span className=\"text-xs text-white/80\">1 week ago</span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-white mb-2 leading-relaxed\">Q3 OKR Drafting</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-sm text-white/80 line-clamp-2\">Key objectives discussed during the management sync. Focus on recurring revenue streams.</p>\n            <div className=\"mt-4 flex items-center text-white text-xs font-medium opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">\n              View Note <ChevronRight className=\"w-4 h-4 ml-1\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"bg-teal-700 p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:border-white/40 transition-all cursor-pointer group relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(15,118,110,0.5)]\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n              <span className=\"px-2 py-1 bg-white/20 text-white text-[10px] rounded uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">Soft Skill</span>\n              <span className=\"text-xs text-white/80\">2 weeks ago</span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-white mb-2 leading-relaxed\">Active Listening Framework</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-sm text-white/80 line-clamp-2\">LARA method: Listen, Affirm, Respond, Add. Useful for difficult client conversations.</p>\n            <div className=\"mt-4 flex items-center text-white text-xs font-medium opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">\n               View Note <ChevronRight className=\"w-4 h-4 ml-1\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"bg-rose-700 p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:border-white/40 transition-all cursor-pointer group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(190,18,60,0.5)]\">\n             <div className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:bg-white/30 transition-colors text-white\">\n                <Folder className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n             </div>\n             <h4 className=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-white\">Browse All Notes</h4>\n             <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 mt-1\">42 Total Entries</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"
